   NAME
	WIN - Opens Workbench windows from the Shell/CLI. 

   FORMAT
	WIN <path name>

   TEMPLATE
	(none)

   PATH
	S/WIN

   FUNCTION
	WIN is an ARexx script designed for opening Workbench windows from 
	the Shell/CLI.

   EXAMPLES
	    1>Win sys:expansion

	Will open the Expansion drawer located on the SYS: volume.


   SEE ALSO
	WBLOAD
